---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="Plugins for EmDash — E-Commerce, Leads, Helpdesk & More for EmDash CMS"
	description="Professional plugins for EmDash CMS. Run an online store, capture leads, manage support tickets — all from your EmDash admin panel. The WooCommerce alternative for EmDash."
>
	<!-- Nav -->
	<nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 border-b border-border-subtle bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl">
		<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
			<a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold">
				<span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-600 text-sm font-black text-white">P</span>
				PluginsforEmDash
			</a>
			<div class="hidden items-center gap-8 sm:flex">
				<a href="#plugins" class="text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">Plugins</a>
				<a href="#pricing" class="text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">Pricing</a>
				<a href="#faq" class="text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">FAQ</a>
				<a href="#pricing" class="rounded-lg bg-brand-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-brand-500 transition-colors">Get Started</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<!-- Hero -->
	<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-28">
		<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--color-brand-600)_0%,_transparent_60%)] opacity-15"></div>
		<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
			<div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border-default bg-surface-raised px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-text-secondary">
				<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
				Now available for EmDash CMS v0.1+
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
				Everything you need to
				<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-brand-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">run a business</span>
				on EmDash
			</h1>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-text-secondary sm:text-xl">
				E-commerce, lead capture, helpdesk, and customer service &mdash; purpose-built for EmDash CMS.
				Install in seconds. Your data stays on your infrastructure.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
				<a href="#plugins" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-brand-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-center font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/25 hover:bg-brand-500 transition-all sm:w-auto">
					See All Plugins
				</a>
				<a href="#pricing" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised px-8 py-3.5 text-center font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-surface-overlay transition-all sm:w-auto">
					View Pricing
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Trust bar -->
	<section class="border-y border-border-subtle bg-surface-raised/50 py-8">
		<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-12 gap-y-4 px-6 text-sm text-text-muted">
			<span>Sandboxed &amp; Secure</span>
			<span>One-Click Install</span>
			<span>Works on Cloudflare Workers &amp; Node.js</span>
			<span>Your Data, Your Server</span>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Plugins -->
	<section id="plugins" class="py-20 sm:py-28">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">The plugin suite</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">Everything you need to turn your EmDash site into a business platform.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
				<!-- Commerce -->
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-8 transition-all hover:border-green-500/50 sm:col-span-2">
					<div class="sm:flex sm:gap-8">
						<div class="sm:flex-1">
							<div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">
								<svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z"></path></svg>
							</div>
							<div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Commerce</h3>
								<span class="rounded-full bg-green-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-green-400">Available Now</span>
							</div>
							<p class="mb-6 text-text-secondary">
								The WooCommerce alternative for EmDash. Run a full online store with products, variants, shopping cart, Stripe checkout, order management, customers, discount codes, and inventory tracking.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="sm:flex-1">
							<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Products with variants, images &amp; categories</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Shopping cart &amp; Stripe Checkout</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Order management &amp; inventory tracking</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Discount codes (percentage, fixed, free shipping)</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Customer records &amp; lifetime value</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="mt-4 rounded-lg border border-border-subtle bg-surface p-3">
								<p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-1">Pro features:</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Stripe Connect &middot; Customer emails &middot; Abandoned cart recovery &middot; Analytics dashboard &middot; Digital downloads &middot; WooCommerce import</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Forms -->
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-8 transition-all hover:border-brand-600/50">
					<div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-600/10 text-brand-400">
						<svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Forms</h3>
						<span class="rounded-full bg-green-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-green-400">Available Now</span>
					</div>
					<p class="mb-6 text-text-secondary">
						Build forms, collect submissions, and optionally manage leads with a full CRM pipeline. Templates for contact, feedback, and newsletter forms.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Form builder with templates</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Honeypot + Turnstile spam protection</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Webhook forwarding &amp; CSV export</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Email notifications</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400 mt-1">&#10003;</span> Pro CRM: lead pipeline &amp; scoring</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Pricing -->
	<section id="pricing" class="py-20 sm:py-28">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Pricing</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">Every plugin is free to use. Upgrade per plugin for premium features.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Commerce Pricing -->
			<div class="mt-16">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">
						<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z"></path></svg>
					</span>
					Commerce
				</h3>
				<div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
					<!-- Commerce Free -->
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold">Free</h4>
						<div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">$0</span>
							<span class="text-text-muted">/forever</span>
						</div>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">Full store with your own Stripe keys. No transaction fee.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Unlimited products &amp; orders</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Cart &amp; Stripe Checkout</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Order management</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Discount codes</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Inventory tracking</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Customer records</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Admin notifications</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="https://github.com/pluginsforemdash/commerce" class="mt-6 block rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-surface-overlay transition-colors">
							Install Free
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Commerce Pro -->
					<div class="relative rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-600 bg-surface-raised p-6">
						<div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-brand-600 px-3 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white">Best Value</div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold">Pro</h4>
						<div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">$29</span>
							<span class="text-text-muted">/month</span>
						</div>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">Your own Stripe keys. 0% transaction fee. All Pro features.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-text-primary font-medium"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Everything in Free</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Customer order emails</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Shipping confirmation emails</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Abandoned cart recovery</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Analytics dashboard</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Digital downloads</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> WooCommerce import</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="/buy" class="mt-6 block rounded-xl bg-brand-600 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/25 hover:bg-brand-500 transition-colors">
							Get Pro
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Commerce Pro Connect -->
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold">Pro Connect</h4>
						<div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">$19</span>
							<span class="text-text-muted">/mo + 1.5%</span>
						</div>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">Managed Stripe Connect. No keys to set up. All Pro features.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-text-primary font-medium"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> All Pro features</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Stripe Connect (managed)</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> No API key setup</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> One-click onboarding</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Lower monthly cost</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Priority support</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="/buy" class="mt-6 block rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-surface-overlay transition-colors">
							Get Pro Connect
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Forms Pricing -->
			<div class="mt-16">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-600/10 text-brand-400">
						<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
					</span>
					Forms
				</h3>
				<div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
					<!-- Forms Free -->
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold">Free</h4>
						<div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">$0</span>
							<span class="text-text-muted">/forever</span>
						</div>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">Unlimited forms and submissions. Own Resend key for email.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Unlimited forms &amp; submissions</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Form templates</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Spam protection</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Webhooks &amp; CSV export</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Email via own Resend key</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="https://github.com/pluginsforemdash/leads" class="mt-6 block rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-surface-overlay transition-colors">
							Install Free
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Forms Pro -->
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-600 bg-surface-raised p-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold">Pro</h4>
						<div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">$10</span>
							<span class="text-text-muted">/month</span>
						</div>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">Managed email, auto-responders, and analytics.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-text-primary font-medium"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Everything in Free</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Managed email delivery</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Auto-responder emails</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Submission analytics</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> 5,000 emails/month</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="/buy" class="mt-6 block rounded-xl bg-brand-600 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/25 hover:bg-brand-500 transition-colors">
							Get Pro
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Forms Pro CRM -->
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold">Pro CRM</h4>
						<div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">$29</span>
							<span class="text-text-muted">/month</span>
						</div>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">Full lead pipeline, scoring, and contact management.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-text-primary font-medium"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Everything in Pro</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Lead pipeline</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Lead scoring &amp; assignment</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Contact records</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-400">&#10003;</span> Activity log &amp; notes</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="/buy" class="mt-6 block rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-surface-overlay transition-colors">
							Get Pro CRM
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How It Works -->
	<section class="border-y border-border-subtle bg-surface-raised/30 py-20 sm:py-28">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Up and running in 60 seconds</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">Standard EmDash plugins. No external services to set up.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-16 space-y-12">
				<div class="flex gap-6">
					<div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-sm font-bold text-white">1</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Install the plugin</h3>
						<div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface p-4">
							<code class="text-sm text-brand-300">npm install emdash-plugin-commerce</code>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex gap-6">
					<div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-sm font-bold text-white">2</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Add it to your config</h3>
						<div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface p-4 overflow-x-auto">
							<pre class="text-sm text-text-secondary">import &#123; commercePlugin &#125; from "emdash-plugin-commerce";

export default defineConfig(&#123;
  integrations: [
    emdash(&#123;
      plugins: [commercePlugin()],
    &#125;),
  ],
&#125;);</pre>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex gap-6">
					<div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-sm font-bold text-white">3</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Add your Stripe key and start selling</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-text-secondary">
							Add products in the admin panel, paste your Stripe key, and your store is live. The plugin handles cart, checkout, inventory, orders, and customers automatically.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why not SaaS? -->
	<section class="border-b border-border-subtle bg-surface-raised/30 py-20 sm:py-28">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Why plugins instead of SaaS?</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-border-default bg-surface-raised p-6">
					<h3 class="font-semibold text-red-400">SaaS tools</h3>
					<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
						<li>Shopify: $39-399/mo + transaction fees</li>
						<li>WooCommerce extensions: $79-299/year each</li>
						<li>HubSpot leads: $20-890/mo</li>
						<li>Data on someone else's servers</li>
						<li>GDPR headaches with third-party processors</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-brand-600/50 bg-surface-raised p-6">
					<h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-400">Our plugins</h3>
					<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
						<li>Free core + $10-29/mo Pro upgrades</li>
						<li>Data stays on your Cloudflare account</li>
						<li>One admin panel for content + business</li>
						<li>Server-rendered, zero client-side bloat</li>
						<li>First-party data, no third parties</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ -->
	<section id="faq" class="py-20 sm:py-28">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
			<h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">FAQ</h2>

			<div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">Do I need to pay to use the plugins?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">No. Every plugin is fully functional for free. Pro upgrades add premium features like managed email, analytics, CRM pipeline, abandoned cart recovery, and digital downloads. Pricing varies per plugin.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">What's the difference between Commerce Pro and Pro Connect?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">Same features. Pro ($29/mo) uses your own Stripe keys with 0% transaction fee &mdash; best for high-volume stores. Pro Connect ($19/mo + 1.5%) uses managed Stripe Connect with no key setup &mdash; best for getting started quickly or lower-volume stores.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">Can I migrate from WooCommerce?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">Yes. Commerce Pro includes a WooCommerce CSV import endpoint. Export your products from WooCommerce, POST the CSV to the import API, and your products appear as drafts for review.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">What is EmDash CMS?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">EmDash is an open-source CMS by Cloudflare, built on Astro. Think of it as the modern successor to WordPress &mdash; serverless, type-safe, with sandboxed plugins. Our plugins extend it with business functionality.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">Where is my data stored?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">All plugin data is stored in your EmDash database (Cloudflare D1, SQLite, or PostgreSQL). We never see or store your data. Pro plans only handle email delivery and payment processing.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">Can I use my own email and payment providers?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">Yes. On free plans, paste your own Resend API key (Leads) or Stripe secret key (Commerce). Or upgrade to Pro for managed delivery with no key setup.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold">Do the plugins work outside Cloudflare?</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">Yes. EmDash runs on any Node.js server with SQLite. Our plugins use the standard plugin API and work everywhere EmDash runs.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
